## Source of Truth

**Single source:** `packages/_redhorn-components/`

This folder:
- Contains Mitosis `.lite.tsx` components
- Is NOT published to npm (private)
- Generates all 4 framework outputs
- Uses underscore prefix to appear first in list

## Generated Packages

These are **auto-generated** by Mitosis:
- `packages/react/src/components/`
- `packages/angular/src/components/`
- `packages/vue/src/components/`
- `packages/react-native/src/components/`

**Never edit generated files directly.**

## Published Packages

These are published to public npm:
- `@redhorn/design-tokens` - Design tokens (CSS + JS)
- `@redhorn/react` - React components
- `@redhorn/angular` - Angular components  
- `@redhorn/vue` - Vue 3 components
- `@redhorn/react-native` - React Native components

## Private Packages

These stay private (not published):
- `@redhorn/redhorn-components` - Source components

